      "explanation": "Fundamental Identities — sin² x + cos² x = 1 (Pythagorean). tan x = sin x / cos x. cot x = cos x / sin x. sec x = 1 / cos x. csc x = 1 / sin x. Double Angle Formulas — sin 2x = 2 sin x cos x. cos 2x = cos² x - sin² x = 2 cos² x - 1 = 1 - 2 sin² x. tan 2x = 2 tan x / (1 - tan² x)."
